WEBVTT

00:01.080 --> 00:02.433
<i>Previously on</i> One Tree Hill.

00:02.520 --> 00:05.159
- Marry me.
- But you can't propose to me.

00:05.320 --> 00:07.470
I was gonna propose to you.

00:09.080 --> 00:12.117
If you tell Whitey I have a heart condition,
I'm off the team.

00:12.200 --> 00:15.476
Yeah, and if I don't tell Whitey about
your heart condition, you're off the planet!

00:15.560 --> 00:17.551
<i>If you weren't so busy</i>
<i>trying to see through her shirt,</i>

00:17.640 --> 00:19.915
you would see through her B.S.
She's using you.

00:20.000 --> 00:23.879
Marry me, Haley. Marry me again
in front of all our friends and our family.

00:23.960 --> 00:27.748
- Pete from Fall Out Boy, you showed.
- Didn't anyone think I was gonna show?

00:27.840 --> 00:29.319
Sorry, this cabinet's off-limits.

00:29.400 --> 00:31.595
- What's in there?
- It's just private.

00:31.680 --> 00:33.398
<i>Probably should go</i>
<i>sleep on the couch, though.</i>

00:33.480 --> 00:36.438
<i>Yeah, you should, but you're not going to.</i>

00:37.080 --> 00:38.832
<i>Brooke Davis, are you threatening me?</i>

00:38.920 --> 00:41.275
Let's just say payback's a bitch.

